_104zne1665702701420.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zne1665702701420.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zne1665702701420.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zne1665702701420\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $ocxhandle\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zne1665702701420___ocxhandle_279228\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the handle of the requested OCX object.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zne1665702701420__topic_d87332e1_d87333e1_d87334e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zne1665702701420__p_d87335e1_d87336e1_d87337e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ocxhandle</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zne1665702701420__topic_d58152e1_d58153e1_d58154e1_d58155e1_d58156e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1022800e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9323e1_d9324e1_d9325e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9323e1_d9324e1_d9325e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9323e1_d9324e1_d9325e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9323e1_d9324e1_d9325e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9323e1_d9324e1_d9325e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9323e1_d9324e1_d9325e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9323e1_d9324e1_d9325e1__entry__3\">\n Field name; mandatory.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zne1665702701420__topic_d58157e1_d58158e1_d58159e1_d58160e1_d58161e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1022800e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zne1665702701420__li_d35117e1_d35118e1_d35119e1\">Handle of the OCX object encapsulated in the OCX container widget.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zne1665702701420__li_d35120e1_d35121e1_d35122e1\">A NULL handle is returned if <var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> is not an OCX object or if an error occurs during the evaluation of this function. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occhandle</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__1\">\n -1101\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UPROCERR_FIELD</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__3\">\n An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__1\">\n -1102\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UPROCERR_ENTITY</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zne1665702701420__table_d9326e1_d9327e1_d9328e1__entry__3\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zne1665702701420__topic_d58162e1_d58163e1_d58164e1_d58165e1_d58166e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1022800e228\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zne1665702701420__d5909e20\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534519\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534519\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$ocxhandle Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $ocxhandle Return the handle of the requested OCX object. $ocxhandle ( Field ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Field String Field name; mandatory. Return Values Handle of the OCX object encapsulated in the OCX container widget. A NULL handle is returned if Field is not an OCX object or if an error occurs during the evaluation of this function. $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $occhandle Value Error constant Meaning -1101 UPROCERR_FIELD An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. -1102 UPROCERR_ENTITY The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Use in Form components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}